<h1>HTTP400</h1>
<p>Either passed in irrelevant/faulty data (such as text instead of numbers), or a server error</p>
<p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_HTTP_status_codes" style="color: blue; text-decoration: underline">Wikipedia Definition:</a> The server cannot or will not process the request due to an apparent client error (e.g., malformed request syntax, size too large, invalid request message framing, or deceptive request routing).</p>